            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>
                    <persName corresp="#gaudentius" xml:lang="la">Aurelius Gaudentius</persName> and <persName corresp="#martina" xml:lang="la">Martina</persName> commissioned for themselves in their lifetime.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If anyone should inflict injury on it, he will give to the <term xml:lang="la">fiscus</term> <measure type="fine" unit="roman_pound" commodity="gold" quantity="1"> one roman pound of gold.</measure>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p><persName corresp="#gaudentius" xml:lang="la">Aurelius Gaudentius</persName> e <persName corresp="#martina" xml:lang="la">Martina</persName>, da vivi comprarono [l'arca].</p>
                <p>Se qualcuno [arrecherà] loro offesa, versi una libbra d’oro.</p>
            </div>
